text: Pakubuhono III, (born 2009) or his personal name Chun Doo-hyo (Korean: 전두효), is the thrid Susuhunan (Monarch) of Indragiri since May 2022. He was a founder of the New Wave Party, an self-proclaimed centrist-wing political party in Itaewon that was formed by His Majesty Tuanku Sri Maharaja Lela Bendahara Pakubuhono III himself in 31 August 2022. ==References== Category:2009 births Category:Living people Category:Monarchs
title: Pakubuhono III
